| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5567 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9cd7488e-3aa7-5301-b27f-ba21191f40c6"
